  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  x-ray verified knee osteoarthritis (Kellegren &amp; Lawrence grade I-III)

          -  Loss of function and withstanding pain &gt;3 months

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  physical therapy treatment during the last 3 months

          -  knee injury

          -  inflammatory arthritis

          -  symptoms from the hip joints greater than the knee pain

          -  planned knee surgery the next 6 months

          -  heart and lung disorders or other health issues affecting the ability to complete the
             intervention
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
